title: Little Black Duck Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Fast food, Take-out only, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little lunch window in the wall of Foodworks grocery store. Offers good-size burgers including ones with vegetarian or vegan patty when you ask. Also deli salads, coffee. Inside is open 7days until late, but the takeaway cafe window itself is only open for lunch.
